                     <interp inst="t17841208-20-person388" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , when he came to me he did not belong to any ship, he was discharged from the Medway to Hasler hospital; and from thence he went to the Mars, after he was discharged unserviceable from there, he came to me to make him out a power of attorney, to receive some prize money for the Medway, I saw him sign this, I received some prize money, one pound two shillings and six-pence.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841208-20-person389">
                  JAMES
                   WARD
               <interp inst="t17841208-20-person389" type="surname" value="WARD"></interp>
